attr.title: Fares
attr.desc: Join the blue haired treasure hunter Fares in the adventure of a lifetime in this retro inspired 16-bit platformer. Discover hidden treasures and artifacts as you travel through dangerous lands of a lost civilization. Can you complete Fares collection? See if you can in this colorful and cute adventure!
attr.inst: Purchase the game on Steam and copy all files into the assets folder.
attr.inst_md: Purchase the game on [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/1094070/Fares/) and copy all files into the `assets` folder.
